The associated diff file contains the diff of the below bugs

	https://bugs.launchpad.net/neutron/+bug/1312016
	https://bugs.launchpad.net/nova/+bug/1522112
	https://bugs.launchpad.net/nova/+bug/1467581
	https://bugs.launchpad.net/nova/+bug/1501735
	https://bugs.launchpad.net/nova/+bug/1407664

The base versions of the nova & neturon packages on top of which this patch can be applied is

	ii  neutron-common                      2:7.0.4-0ubuntu1~cloud0               all          Neutron is a virtual network service for Openstack - common
	ii  neutron-plugin-linuxbridge-agent    2:7.0.4-0ubuntu1~cloud0               all          Neutron is a virtual network service for Openstack - linuxbridge plugin agent
	ii  neutron-plugin-ml2                  2:7.0.4-0ubuntu1~cloud0               all          Neutron is a virtual network service for Openstack - ML2 plugin
	ii  neutron-plugin-openvswitch-agent    2:7.0.4-0ubuntu1~cloud0               all          Neutron is a virtual network service for Openstack - Open vSwitch plugin agent
	ii  neutron-plugin-sriov-agent          2:7.0.4-0ubuntu1~cloud0               all          Neutron is a virtual network service for Openstack - IBM agent
	ii  nova-common                         2:12.0.3-0ubuntu1~cloud0              all          OpenStack Compute - common files
	ii  nova-compute                        2:12.0.3-0ubuntu1~cloud0              all          OpenStack Compute - compute node base
	ii  nova-compute-kvm                    2:12.0.3-0ubuntu1~cloud0              all          OpenStack Compute - compute node (KVM)
	ii  nova-compute-libvirt                2:12.0.3-0ubuntu1~cloud0              all          OpenStack Compute - compute node libvirt support
	ii  python-neutron                      2:7.0.4-0ubuntu1~cloud0               all          Neutron is a virtual network service for Openstack - Python library
	ii  python-neutron-fwaas                1:7.0.2-0ubuntu1~cloud0               all          Firewall-as-a-Service driver for OpenStack Neutron
	ii  python-neutronclient                1:3.1.0-0ubuntu1~cloud0               all          client API library for Neutron
	ii  python-nova                         2:12.0.3-0ubuntu1~cloud0              all          OpenStack Compute Python libraries
	ii  python-novaclient                   2:2.30.1-1~cloud0                     all          client library for OpenStack Compute API

Please follow the below steps to apply the patch

	1. Install nova & neutron components from cloud-archive liberty
	2. Make sure the installed nova & neutron package versions are same as given above
	3. cd to the dist-package directory (cd /usr/lib/python2.7/dist-packages)
	4. Verify that patch patches cleanly (sudo patch --dry-run -p0 -i <path-to-openstack-fixes-diff>)
	5. Apply the patch (sudo patch -p0 -b -i <path-to-openstack-fixes-diff>)
	6. verify that there are no failures in the patch
	7. Restart the nova & neutron services
